"7:111:1" : {s: 7, a: 111, w: 1, r: "قول", t: "قَالُوٓا۟", l: "قَالَ", lc: 1618, tl: "qālū", lb: "কথা বলা",e: "They said", b: "তারা বলে", i: "mereka berkata", f: 250, rm: "to say/speak, to call, to be named, word/speech, utterance, a thing said, greeting, discourse, one who says/speaks. To inspire/transmit/relate/answer/think/profess, emit an opinion on, indicate a state or condition or circumstance. qailun - speaker, indicator.", ag: "فعل ماض وضمير متصل ", eg: "Verb Perfect and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "PERF", qual: "", deg: "3", gen: "M", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "قَالَ،قَآئِلٌۭ،قَوْلٌۭ"},
"7:111:2" : {s: 7, a: 111, w: 2, r: "رجو", t: "أَرْجِهْ", l: "تُرْجِى", lc: 3, tl: "arjih", lb: "স্থগিত করা, বিলম্বিত করণ,",e: "Postpone him", b: "অবকাশ দাও", i: "tahanlah ia", f: 2, rm: "to hope/expect, an opinion requiring the happening of an event in which will be a cause of happiness; expectation of deriving advantage from an event of which a cause has already occurred, keep awaited, put off, put aside, defer/delay, fear, beg/request. arja (pl.) - borders, sides. marjowwon is a person in whom great hopes are placed (e.g. 11:62).", ag: "فعل أمر صيغة ٤ وضمير متصل ", eg: "Verb Imperative 4th form and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "IMPV", qual: "(IV)", deg: "2", gen: "M", num: "S", mood: "", lu: "مُرْجَوْنَ،يَرْجُوا۟،تُرْجِى"},
"7:111:3" : {s: 7, a: 111, w: 3, r: "اخو", t: "وَأَخَاهُ", l: "أَخ", lc: 75, tl: "wa-akhāhu", lb: "ভাই",e: "and his brother", b: "ও তার ভাইকে", i: "dan saudaranya", f: 3, rm: "Male person having the same parents as another or a male only having one parent in common; person of the same descent/land/creed/faith with others; brother; friend; companion; match; fellow of a pair; kinsman; intimately acquainted.", ag: "واو عطف وأسم منصوب وضمير متصل ", eg: "Conjunction wa and Noun Accusative case and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "N", pos: "N", att: "ACC", qual: "", deg: "", gen: "M", num: "S", mood: "", lu: "أَخٌ،أُخْتٌۭ"},
"7:111:4" : {s: 7, a: 111, w: 4, r: "رسل", t: "وَأَرْسِلْ", l: "أَرْسَلَ", lc: 130, tl: "wa-arsil", lb: "পাঠানো, বার্তা পাঠানো",e: "and send", b: "পাঠান", i: "dan kirimlah", f: 1, rm: "to send a messenger, bestow, let go. rasul (pl. rusul) - envoy, bearer of a message, messenger. risalat - message, commission, mission, epistle. arsala (vb. 4) - to send. mursalat (pl. of mursalatun) - those sent forth.", ag: "واو عطف وفعل أمر صيغة ٤", eg: "Conjunction wa and Verb Imperative 4th form", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "IMPV", qual: "(IV)", deg: "2", gen: "M", num: "S", mood: "", lu: "أَرْسَلَ،أُرْسِلَ،رُسُلٌۭ،رَسُولٌۭ،رَسُولُ"},
